RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 1 1M Dirt CR: 43. Maiden Special Weight Purse 10810. FOR NATIVE MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 118 lbs.; Older, 121 lbs. 2# A clasf. inferior y debts Allowed 2 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: REY YAIR drew off. CATALIZADOR second best. EL SOSPECHOSO pressed pace, led, weakened. EL SERIO dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 2 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 37. Maiden Claiming Purse 9016. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. 2# A clasf.$27,000 Allowed 2 lbs. 4# A clasf. inferior y debts Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $27,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: RAMWIL'S CHROME cleared, lasted. EL ZAFIRO late kick, short. WOODVILLE'S MUSIC short. KLIMT'S LEGACY grudgingly. LOOKIN AT ME trailed.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 3 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 49. Maiden Claiming Purse 5880. FOR MAIDENS, THREE YEARS OLD AND UPWARD. Three Year Olds, 120 lbs.; Older, 123 lbs. Non-winners Of Races Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: HATCHET JACK off slowly, driving. SUPER ASTRO led, caught. GIANT GOLD late gain. SLEW FANTASY set pace, weakened. SIR ROBERT dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 4 6F Dirt CR: 40. Claiming Purse 7938. FOR FILLIES THREE YEARS OLD. Weight, 120 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 4 Allowed 2 lbs. A Race Since December 4 Allowed 4 lbs. Claiming Price $20,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: MUNIGANS close up, led, driving. BELLA LARGO grudgingly. BELLEZA MORENA gaining. DREAM V. vied for lead, tired late. ATOMIC BLUE dropped back.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 5 5 1/2F Dirt CR: 63. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FOUR YEAR OLDS AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NEVER WON TWO RACES AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 19 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since January 4 Allowed 3 lbs. A Race Since December 4 Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PAPIS INTUITION rallied, driving. POKER COCO close up, second best. FUN LOADED vied for lead, grudgingly. CAMPECHANO middle of pack, evenly. NAPAJ improved position. LIBRE SOY middle of pack, no rally. GEOSCIENCE pressed pace, weakened. MISTER PILOT pressed pace, weakened. RUN HAPPY STAR checked rail. FURY STORM failed to menace. EL GRAN CACAO failed to menace. MORO CAT off slowly, no menace. WRITER'S EXPRESS failed to menace. SHOPPING lost jockey 3/8 pole.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 6 6F Dirt CR: 66. Claiming Purse 6000. FOR FILLIES AND MARES FOUR YEARS OLD AND UPWARD WHICH HAVE NOT WON A RACE SINCE AUGUST 4 AND WHICH HAVE STARTED FOR A CLAIMING PRICE OF $8,000 OR LESS. Weight, 121 lbs. 5# A clasf.$4,000 y debts Allowed 5 lbs. Claiming Price $4,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: I'LLMAKEYOUSMILE stalked pace, rallied, driving. VENEZIA MIRANDA chased, led, second best. SKY CHASER some late gain. ECLIPTICALS TALKIN improved position. CYBERICA off slowly, finished well. APPEALING LALIBELA improved position. BATTLE RHYTHM set pace, weakened. PEGGY'S COVE failed to menace. KANTARITA failed to menace. MISS MAC off slowly, no menace.

RACE.RACE_TEXT: RACE 7 1 1/16M Dirt CR: 45. Allowance Purse 14896. FOR NATIVE FILLIES THREE YEARS OLD. Weight, 118 lbs. Non-winners Of A Race Since January 4 Allowed 1 lbs. A Race Since December 4 Allowed 2 lbs.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: PRESTIGIOSA led, prevailed. COPA DE ORO steady attack. JAIMANITAS BEACH loomed, flattened out. SIGMA ALPHA set pace, drew clear, weakened. SYRIA MARIE trailed.
